{"tid":486484,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"豬西唔知接唔接受好仔","createTime":"2017-12-02T02:04:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-02T02:37:27.000Z","uid":51719,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d22d8240fa356b13fcb87105c6f0b7894a110954","tid":486484,"uid":51719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T02:04:37.000Z","msg":"見個豬西講到自己如何瞓街做黃絲，因此一本正經要考慮一星期，先知接唔接受條件人品好過佢十條街嘅男仔，因為佢覺人哋係藍絲。<br />\n<br />\n見到有二千幾人屌佢，覺得好開心。原來連登仔多係有腦嘅，冇人屌你係藍絲白絲， 大家可以順便望下，所謂嘅黃絲，正正就多呢啲不知所謂，感情同賣西都唔識分嘅垃圾。 可能我自己撞啱，見親大大聲話自己黃絲嘅，十個有八九個都好似呢挺癡癡地。"},{"pid":"53f682ff9ae40c74b7e2e8f911186144e55211cb","tid":486484,"uid":150098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T02:08:06.000Z","msg":"你不如直接表達想講D乜啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ebc4c95a436d8384c9d3eecaee3a762c1d1c608","tid":486484,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T02:18:50.000Z","msg":"有底線都唔啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57ed74aa49efa139c82e6ae64cf01f06b656537d","tid":486484,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T02:21:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有底線都唔啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要考慮就唔叫有底線啦"},{"pid":"5c7ba73e1136dd45aa19a0ad7108dd93e8763bd9","tid":486484,"uid":99048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T02:29:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有底線都唔啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要考慮就唔叫有底線啦</blockquote><br />\n又多士喇你"},{"pid":"5fd64bc7eb1796bed5c0e8bb4f38522917492119","tid":486484,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T02:37:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有底線都唔啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要考慮就唔叫有底線啦</blockquote><br />\n又多士喇你</blockquote><br />\n我係多土"},{"pid":"bd8c62